  <brief_title>Placebo-controlled, Dose-escalation Study of the Safety of IMO-2125 in Hepatitis C-infected Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Multi-center, Placebo-controlled, Dose-escalation Study of the Safety of IMO-2125 in Hepatitis C-infected Patients Unresponsive to Standard Treatment With Pegylated Interferon and Ribavirin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
